hpicfRpvstMIB.name: hpicfRpvstMIB

revisions.description: Added object hpicfRpvstPortIeeeRstBpdu. Deprecated compliance hpicfRpvstCompliance1. Added compliance hpicfRpvstCompliance3. Deprecated group hpicfRpvstPortGroup. Added hpicfRpvstPortGroup1.

Added objects hpicfRpvstLogPortStateTransitions, hpicfRpvstNewPortRole, hpicfRpvstOldPortRole, hpicfRpvstPathCostMode, hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeCurrentPortRole, hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeEntry, hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeIndex, hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangePreviousPortRole, hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeTable, hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeTime, hpicfRpvstPortVlanInconsistencyReason, hpicfRpvstSendTopoChangeCtrl, hpicfRpvstTopoChangeTime, hpicfRpvstTopologyChange, hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxEntry, hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxIndex, hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxMacAddress, hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxPortId, hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxTable, hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxTime, hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxCurrentPortRole, hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxEntry, hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxIndex, hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxPortId, hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxPreviousPortRole, hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxTable, hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxTime. Added groups hpicfRpvstPvst1, hpicfRpvstNotificationGroupPvst1, hpicfRpvstNotificationObjectGrpPvst1, hpicfRpvstTopologyRxGroup, hpicfRpvstTopologyTxGroup, hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeGroup. Added complaince hpicfRpvstCompliance2.
Initial version of this MIB module

hpicfRpvstMIB.contactinfo: Hewlett-Packard Company 8000 Foothills Blvd. Roseville, CA 95747
hpicfRpvstMIB.description: The MIB module Rapid Per VLAN Spanning Tree(RPVST).

PointToPoint.name: PointToPoint
PointToPoint.description: forceTrue: This value indicates that the administrator requires the MAC to be treated as if it is connected to a point-to-point LAN segment, regardless of any indications to the contrary that are generated by the MAC entity. forceFalse: This value indicates that the administrator requires the MAC to be treated as if it is connected to a non-point-to-point LAN segment, regardless of any indications to the contrary that are generated by the MAC entity. auto: This value indicates that the administrator requires the point-to-point status of the MAC to be determined in accordance with the specific MAC procedures defined in 6.5.

hpicfRpvstResetCounters.name: hpicfRpvstResetCounters
hpicfRpvstResetCounters.description: Setting this object to true(1) will reset all the RPVST counters. Setting this to false(2) is no operation.

hpicfRpvstExtendedSystemID.name: hpicfRpvstExtendedSystemID
hpicfRpvstExtendedSystemID.description: Indicates whether Extended System ID feature is enabled or not.

hpicfRpvstIgnorePVIDInconsistency.name: hpicfRpvstIgnorePVIDInconsistency
hpicfRpvstIgnorePVIDInconsistency.description: Setting this object to True(1) will enable RPVST to run on mismatched PVID links.Once set it will apply to all RPVST instances

hpicfRpvstPathCostMode.name: hpicfRpvstPathCostMode
hpicfRpvstPathCostMode.description: hpicfRpvstPathCostMode controls which pathcost mode to use. A device can function in one of the 2 modes defined below. pathCost8021d - The device calculates the default path cost for ports based on IEEE 802.1d. pathCost8021t - The device calculates the default path cost for ports based on IEEE 802.1t. proprietary -The device calculates the default path cost for ports based on the proprietary standard. Link Speed Vs Pathcost Table ---------------------------------------------------------- |Link speed| Pathcost in | Pathcost in | Pathcost in | | | IEEE802.1d | IEEE 802.1t | private standard| ---------------------------------------------------------- | 0 | 65535 | 200,000,000 | 200,000 | ---------------------------------------------------------- | 10 Mbps | 100 | 2,000,000 | 2,000 | ---------------------------------------------------------- | 100 Mbp | 19 | 200,000 | 200 | ---------------------------------------------------------- | 1000 Mbp | 4 | 20,000 | 20 | ---------------------------------------------------------- | 10 Gbps | 2 | 2,000 | 2 | ----------------------------------------------------------

hpicfRpvstVlanTable.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTable
hpicfRpvstVlanTable.description: Information describing the RPVST configuration and statistics of the VLANs.

hpicfRpvstVlanEntry.name: hpicfRpvstVlanEntry
hpicfRpvstVlanEntry.description: Information describing the RPVST configuration and statistics of each of the VLANs.

hpicfRpvstVlanId.name: hpicfRpvstVlanId
hpicfRpvstVlanId.description: A VLAN ID to uniquely identifying the entries.

hpicfRpvstVlanHelloTime.name: hpicfRpvstVlanHelloTime
hpicfRpvstVlanHelloTime.description: The amount of time between the transmission of configuration BPDUs by this node on any port in this VLAN when it is root of the spanning tree, or trying to become so for this VLAN.

hpicfRpvstVlanForwardDelay.name: hpicfRpvstVlanForwardDelay
hpicfRpvstVlanForwardDelay.description: The amount of time between transitioning from listening to learning and learning to forwarding by this node on any port when it is acting as a root for this VLAN.

hpicfRpvstVlanMaxAge.name: hpicfRpvstVlanMaxAge
hpicfRpvstVlanMaxAge.description: The maximum age of RPVST information learned from the network on any port before it is discarded.

hpicfRpvstVlanPriority.name: hpicfRpvstVlanPriority
hpicfRpvstVlanPriority.description: The value of the write-able portion of the Bridge ID (i.e., the first two octets of the (8 octet long) Bridge ID). The other (last) 6 octets of the Bridge ID are given by the value dot1dBridgeBaseAddress.

hpicfRpvstVlanRoot.name: hpicfRpvstVlanRoot
hpicfRpvstVlanRoot.description: To explicitly configure this switch to be primary/secondary root for this VLAN.

hpicfRpvstVlanRpvstStatus.name: hpicfRpvstVlanRpvstStatus
hpicfRpvstVlanRpvstStatus.description: To enable/disable RPVST on the VLAN.

hpicfRpvstVlanResetCounters.name: hpicfRpvstVlanResetCounters
hpicfRpvstVlanResetCounters.description: Setting this object to true(1) will reset the RPVST counters for this VLAN.

hpicfRpvstVlanOperHelloTime.name: hpicfRpvstVlanOperHelloTime
hpicfRpvstVlanOperHelloTime.description: The amount of time between the transmission of BPDUs by this node on any port in this VLAN when it is root of the spanning tree, or trying to become so for this VLAN. This is the actual value that this bridge is using.

hpicfRpvstVlanRootPriority.name: hpicfRpvstVlanRootPriority
hpicfRpvstVlanRootPriority.description: The priority of root bridge in this VLAN.

hpicfRpvstVlanRootPort.name: hpicfRpvstVlanRootPort
hpicfRpvstVlanRootPort.description: The root port for this VLAN.

hpicfRpvstVlanRootPathCost.name: hpicfRpvstVlanRootPathCost
hpicfRpvstVlanRootPathCost.description: The path cost to the Root from this bridge in this VLAN.

hpicfRpvstVlanRootMacAddress.name: hpicfRpvstVlanRootMacAddress
hpicfRpvstVlanRootMacAddress.description: MAC address of the Root in this VLAN.

hpicfRpvstVlanRootChangeCounter.name: hpicfRpvstVlanRootChangeCounter
hpicfRpvstVlanRootChangeCounter.description: The number of times the root has changed for this VLAN.

hpicfRpvstVlanTimeSinceLastTopoChange.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTimeSinceLastTopoChange
hpicfRpvstVlanTimeSinceLastTopoChange.description: The time (in hundredths of a second) since the last time a topology change was detected by the bridge entity for this VLAN.

hpicfVlanTopoChangeCount.name: hpicfVlanTopoChangeCount
hpicfVlanTopoChangeCount.description: The total number of topology changes detected by this bridge in this VLAN since the management entity was last reset or initialized.

hpicfRpvstSendTopoChangeCtrl.name: hpicfRpvstSendTopoChangeCtrl
hpicfRpvstSendTopoChangeCtrl.description: Setting this object to true(1) will enable sending of SNMP notifications for all topology change events on this VLAN.

hpicfRpvstLogPortStateTransitions.name: hpicfRpvstLogPortStateTransitions
hpicfRpvstLogPortStateTransitions.description: Setting this object to true(1) will enable event logging of PVST port state transitions for this VLAN.

hpicfRpvstPortTable.name: hpicfRpvstPortTable
hpicfRpvstPortTable.description: Information describing the RPVST specific configuration and statistics of the ports.

hpicfRpvstPortEntry.name: hpicfRpvstPortEntry
hpicfRpvstPortEntry.description: Information describing the RPVST specific configuration and statistics of the ports.

hpicfRpvstPortAdminEdge.name: hpicfRpvstPortAdminEdge
hpicfRpvstPortAdminEdge.description: The administrative value of the Edge Port parameter. A value of true(1) indicates that this port should be assumed as an edge-port, and a value of false(2) indicates that this port should be assumed as a non-edge-port. Note that even when this object's value is true(1), the hpicfRpvstOperEdgePort can be false(2) if a BPDU has been received.

hpicfRpvstPortAutoEdge.name: hpicfRpvstPortAutoEdge
hpicfRpvstPortAutoEdge.description: It is used by the Bridge detection state machine for the automatic identification of edge ports.

hpicfRpvstPortBpduFiltering.name: hpicfRpvstPortBpduFiltering
hpicfRpvstPortBpduFiltering.description: This value indicates whether or not BPDUs need to be filtered on this port. If the value is true(1) the received BPDUs will be dropped and no BPDUs will be transmitted on the port. If the value is false (2) the BPDUs will be processed as usual.

hpicfRpvstPortRestrictedTcn.name: hpicfRpvstPortRestrictedTcn
hpicfRpvstPortRestrictedTcn.description: This value indicates whether or not to propagate topology changes to other ports. true(1) causes the port not to propagate topology changes to other ports.

hpicfRpvstPortRootGuard.name: hpicfRpvstPortRootGuard
hpicfRpvstPortRootGuard.description: Setting this object to true(1) forces port to not to be selected as root port even if this port has best spanning-tree.

hpicfRpvstPortLoopGuard.name: hpicfRpvstPortLoopGuard
hpicfRpvstPortLoopGuard.description: Setting this object to true(1) causes the forwarding port to move to the blocking state and prevent the blocking port to move to forwarding state when no BPDUs are received, instead goes to loop inconsistent state.

hpicfRpvstPortBpduProtection.name: hpicfRpvstPortBpduProtection
hpicfRpvstPortBpduProtection.description: Setting this true (1) indicates that no BPDUs are expected to be received on this port. At the reception of BPDUs the BPDU protection mechanism will disable this port and port will transition into bpduError state.

hpicfRpvstPortIeeeRstBpdu.name: hpicfRpvstPortIeeeRstBpdu
hpicfRpvstPortIeeeRstBpdu.description: The hpicfRpvstPortIeeeRstBpdu controls, on a per port basis, whether or not IEEE RST BPDUs will be transmitted and received on VLANs that the port is an untagged member of. The value true(1) means that the port will allow transmission and reception of IEEE RST BPDUs on ports untagged to a VLAN while false(2) means it will not.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTable.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTable
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTable.description: Information describing the RPVST configuration and statistics of the ports in the given VLAN.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanEntry.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanEntry
hpicfRpvstPortVlanEntry.description: Information describing the RPVST configuration and statistics of the ports in the given VLAN.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanPathCost.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanPathCost
hpicfRpvstPortVlanPathCost.description: The contribution of this port to the path cost of paths towards the root which include this port. auto(0)

hpicfRpvstPortVlanPriority.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanPriority
hpicfRpvstPortVlanPriority.description: The value of the port priority field that is contained in the first (in network byte order) octet of the (2 octet long) Port ID.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanResetCounters.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanResetCounters
hpicfRpvstPortVlanResetCounters.description: Setting this object to true(1) will reset the RPVST counters for this port-vlan pair. Get on this object will always return false(2)

hpicfRpvstPortVlanRole.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanRole
hpicfRpvstPortVlanRole.description: Role played by the port in a given VLAN.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanState.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanState
hpicfRpvstPortVlanState.description: The port's current state. This state controls what action a port takes on reception of a frame.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanDesigBridge.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanDesigBridge
hpicfRpvstPortVlanDesigBridge.description: The Bridge Identifier of the bridge that this port considers to be the Designated Bridge for this port's segment.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanOperPointToPoint.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanOperPointToPoint
hpicfRpvstPortVlanOperPointToPoint.description: true : This value indicates that the MAC is connected to a point-to-point LAN segment; i.e., there is at most one other system attached to the LAN segment. false: This value indicates that the MAC is connected to a non-point-to-point LAN segment; i.e., there can be more than one other system attached to the LAN segment.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanOperEdge.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanOperEdge
hpicfRpvstPortVlanOperEdge.description: The operational status of the edge port parameter. A value of true(1) indicates that this port should be assumed as an edge-port, and a value of false(2) indicates that this port should be assumed as a non-edge-port.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanInconsistencyReason.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanInconsistencyReason
hpicfRpvstPortVlanInconsistencyReason.description: The reason for which port is blocked by spanning tree protection function.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanRxCountersTable.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanRxCountersTable
hpicfRpvstPortVlanRxCountersTable.description: A table which contains information about each port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanRpvstBpduRx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanRpvstBpduRx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanRpvstBpduRx.description: The number of RPVST BPDUs received on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanRpvstBpduRxLastUpdated.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanRpvstBpduRxLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanRpvstBpduRxLastUpdated.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanRpvstBpduRxCount counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanRstBpduRx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanRstBpduRx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanRstBpduRx.description: The number of RSTP BPDUs received on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanRstBpduRxLastUpdated.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanRstBpduRxLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanRstBpduRxLastUpdated.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanRstBpduRxCount counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanConfigBpduRx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanConfigBpduRx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanConfigBpduRx.description: The number of STP config BPDUs received on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanConfigBpduRxLastUpdate.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanConfigBpduRxLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanConfigBpduRxLastUpdate.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanConfigBpduRxCount counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcnBpduRx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcnBpduRx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcnBpduRx.description: The number of Topology Change Notification BPDUs received on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcnBpduRxLastUpdated.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcnBpduRxLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcnBpduRxLastUpdated.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcnBpduRxCount counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcDetectCount.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcDetectCount
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcDetectCount.description: The number of times Topology Change detected on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcDetectCountLastUpdat.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcDetectCountLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcDetectCountLastUpdat.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcDetectCount counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcFlagRx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcFlagRx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcFlagRx.description: The number of times Topology Change bit was set in the BPDUs received on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcFlagRxLastUpdated.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcFlagRxLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcFlagRxLastUpdated.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcFlagRxCount counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcAckFlagRx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcAckFlagRx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcAckFlagRx.description: The number of times TC-ACK bit was set in the BPDUs received on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcAckFlagRxLastUpdated.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcAckFlagRxLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcAckFlagRxLastUpdated.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcAckFlagRxCount counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanStarvedBpduCount.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanStarvedBpduCount
hpicfRpvstPortVlanStarvedBpduCount.description: The number of times BPDU was not received at scheduled time on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanStarvedBpduCountLastUp.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanStarvedBpduCountLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanStarvedBpduCountLastUp.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanStarvedBpduRxCount counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanInvalidBpduRx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanInvalidBpduRx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanInvalidBpduRx.description: The number of invalid BPDUs received on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanInvalidBpduRxLastUpdat.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanInvalidBpduRxLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanInvalidBpduRxLastUpdat.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanInvalidBpduRxCount counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanLoopedBackBpduRx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanLoopedBackBpduRx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanLoopedBackBpduRx.description: The number of times a BPDU is received on the same port from where it was sent on the same VLAN.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanLoopedBackBpduRxLastUp.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanLoopedBackBpduRxLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanLoopedBackBpduRxLastUp.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanLoopedBackBpduRxCount counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanErrantBpduRxCount.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanErrantBpduRxCount
hpicfRpvstPortVlanErrantBpduRxCount.description: The number of BPDUs received on a BPDU-filtering or BPDU-protected enabled port.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanErrantBpduRxCountLastU.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanErrantBpduRxCountLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanErrantBpduRxCountLastU.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanErrantBpduRxCount counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanAgedBpduRx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanAgedBpduRx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanAgedBpduRx.description: The number of aged BPDUs received on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanAgedBpduRxLastUpdated.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanAgedBpduRxLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanAgedBpduRxLastUpdated.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanAgedBpduRx counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTxCountersTable.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTxCountersTable
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTxCountersTable.description: A table which contains statistics for each port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTxCountersEntry.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTxCountersEntry
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTxCountersEntry.description: A list of statistics for each port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanRpvstBpduTx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanRpvstBpduTx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanRpvstBpduTx.description: The number of RPVST BPDUs sent on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanRpvstBpduTxLastUpdated.description: The time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanBpduTx counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanRstBpduTx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanRstBpduTx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanRstBpduTx.description: The number of RSTP BPDUs sent on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanRstBpduTxLastUpdated.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanRstBpduTxLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanRstBpduTxLastUpdated.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanRstBpduTx was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanConfigBpduTx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanConfigBpduTx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanConfigBpduTx.description: The number of STP config BPDUs sent on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanConfigBpduTxLastUpdate.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanConfigBpduTxLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanConfigBpduTxLastUpdate.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanConfigBpduTx counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcnBpduTx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcnBpduTx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcnBpduTx.description: The number of Topology Change Notification BPDUs sent on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcnBpduTxLastUpdated.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcnBpduTxLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcnBpduTxLastUpdated.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcnBpduTx counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcFlagTx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcFlagTx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcFlagTx.description: The number of times Topology Change bit was set in BPDUs sent on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcFlagTxLastUpdated.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcFlagTxLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcFlagTxLastUpdated.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcFlagTx counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcAckFlagTx.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcAckFlagTx
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcAckFlagTx.description: The number of times TC-ACK bit was set in BPDUs sent on this port-vlan pair.

hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcAckFlagTxLastUpdated.name: hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcAckFlagTxLastUpdated
hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcAckFlagTxLastUpdated.description: Time when hpicfRpvstPortVlanTcAckFlagTx Counter was last updated.

hpicfRpvstVlanRootHistoryTable.name: hpicfRpvstVlanRootHistoryTable
hpicfRpvstVlanRootHistoryTable.description: A table containing the information describing the RPVST root history for each VLAN.

hpicfRpvstVlanRootHistoryEntry.name: hpicfRpvstVlanRootHistoryEntry
hpicfRpvstVlanRootHistoryEntry.description: History of the Roots for the VLANs.

hpicfRpvstVlanRootHistoryIndex.name: hpicfRpvstVlanRootHistoryIndex
hpicfRpvstVlanRootHistoryIndex.description: An index which uniquely identifies a row in root history table.The lowest numerical index always holds the most recent root entry.Currently last 10 entries are supported.

hpicfRpvstVlanRootBridgeId.name: hpicfRpvstVlanRootBridgeId
hpicfRpvstVlanRootBridgeId.description: Root bridge Id consisting of Root priority and Root MAC address.

hpicfRpvstVlanRootHistoryTime.name: hpicfRpvstVlanRootHistoryTime
hpicfRpvstVlanRootHistoryTime.description: Time when a new root was elected.

hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxTable.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxTable
hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxTable.description: A list of entries,one for every topology change event that the switch received on per vlan basis. This table holds entries for last 10 topology change events received on the switch.

hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxEntry.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxEntry
hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxEntry.description: Set of parameters corresponding to topology change event that the switch received on per vlan basis.

hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxIndex.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxIndex
hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxIndex.description: An index which uniquely identifies a row in VLAN TC history table. Currently only last 10 entries are supported.

hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxTime.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxTime
hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxTime.description: Time at which topology change event was received .

hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxMacAddress.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxMacAddress
hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxMacAddress.description: MAC address form which TC change is received.

hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxPortId.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxPortId
hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeRxPortId.description: Port on which an RPVST topology change message is recieved.

hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxTable.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxTable
hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxTable.description: A list of entries,one for every topology change event that switch originated on per vlan basis . This table holds for last 10 topology change events originated on switch

hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxEntry.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxEntry
hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxEntry.description: Set of parameters corresponding to topology change event that switch originated on per vlan basis.

hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxIndex.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxIndex
hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxIndex.description: Agent assigned index to uniquely identify an entry in this table. The lowest numerical index always holds the most recent topoogy change event entry. Currently only last 10 entries are supported.

hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxCurrentPor.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxCurrentPortRole
hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxCurrentPor.description: Current port Role in the topology.

hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxPreviousPo.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxPreviousPortRole
hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxPreviousPo.description: Previous port Role in the topology

hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxTime.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxTime
hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxTime.description: Time at which topology change event was generated.

hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxPortId.name: hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxPortId
hpicfRpvstVlanTopologyChangeTxPortId.description: Port on which an RPVST topology change message originated.

hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeTable.name: hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeTable
hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeTable.description: A table containing the information describing the RPVST port change history.

hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeEntry.name: hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeEntry
hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeEntry.description: History of the port change state.

hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeIndex.name: hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeIndex
hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeIndex.description: An index which uniquely identifies a row in port role change table. Currently only last 10 entries are supported.

hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeTime.name: hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeTime
hpicfRpvstPortRoleChangeTime.description: Time when port role changed took place.

hpicfRpvstErrantBpduDetector.name: hpicfRpvstErrantBpduDetector
hpicfRpvstErrantBpduDetector.description: The identifier of the feature generating Errant BPDU trap.

hpicfRpvstErrantBpduReceived.name: hpicfRpvstErrantBpduReceived
hpicfRpvstErrantBpduReceived.description: This trap generated when an unexpected (errant) BPDU has been received on a port. hpicfRpvstVlanIndex - VLAN instance to which BPDU belongs. hpicfRpvstPortNumber - Port ID on which BPDU received. hpicfRpvstPortVlanErrantBpduRxCount - Total number of errant BPDU received on the port which belongs to VLAN hpicfRpvstVlanId. hpicfRpvstPortState - State of this port. hpicfRpvstPortVlanDesigBridge - Designated Bridge that transmitted this BPDU. hpicfRpvstDesignatedPort - Designated port of the Bridge that transmitted this BPDU. hpicfRpvstErrantBpduSrcMac- Source MAC address of the port sending this Errant trap. hpicfRpvstErrantBpduDetector - The identifier of the feature generating Errant BPDU Trap.

hpicfRpvstNewRoot.name: hpicfRpvstNewRoot
hpicfRpvstNewRoot.description: Trap generated when sending agent has become the new root of spanning Tree for the specified VLAN; the notification is sent by a bridge soon after its election as the new root, e.g., upon expiration of the Topology Change Timer, immediately subsequent to its election. hpicfRpvstVlanIndex - VLAN instance in which new root is elected. hpicfRpvstNewRootBridgeId - Bridge ID of the new root elected. hpicfRpvstPreviousRootBridgeId - Bridge ID of the previous root. hpicfRpvstRootBridgeChangeTimeStamp - Time when the root bridge changed.

hpicfRpvstRootGuardInconsistency.name: hpicfRpvstRootGuardInconsistency
hpicfRpvstRootGuardInconsistency.description: Trap generated when a Root Guard feature enabled port receives superior BPDUs on its interface for a given VLAN instance. hpicfRpvstVlanIndex - Vlan Instance to which BPDU belongs. hpicfRpvstPortNumber - Port ID where root-inconsistency occurred. hpicfRpvstSuperiorBpduSrcMac - The source MAC address of the port sending superior BPDU. hpicfRpvstSuperiorBpduSrcPort - Port belonging to the Bridge, which transmitted the superior BPDU.

hpicfRpvstLoopGuardInconsistency.name: hpicfRpvstLoopGuardInconsistency
hpicfRpvstLoopGuardInconsistency.description: Trap generated when a Loop Guard feature enabled port stops receiving BPDUs from its designated port for a given VLAN instance but keeps the port in blocked state. hpicfRpvstVlanIndex - Vlan Instance in which no BPDU received. hpicfRpvstPortNumber - Port ID where loop-inconsistency occurred. hpicfRpvstPortVlanDesigBridge - Designated Bridge this port was expecting to receive the BPDU.

hpicfRpvstTopologyChange.name: hpicfRpvstTopologyChange
hpicfRpvstTopologyChange.description: Trap generated whenever topology change detected on this port- vlan pair. hpicfRpvstVlanIndex - Vlan Instance for which topology change detected. hpicfRpvstPortNumber - Port ID for which topology change detected. hpicfRpvstOldPortRole - Old role of this port before topology change. hpicfRpvstNewPortRole - New state of this port after topology change. hpicfRpvstTopoChangeTime - Time at which the topology change happened for this port.
